data.description: Large home, large land 1.74 acres/12 lots in the heart of Port Hadlock. Convenient location close to shopping, schools, just down the street from Jefferson County Library. The property is 3/4 fenced and ready for your mini farm, the large garden you have always wanted or maybe some goats? Plenty of covered parking with a large carport and 2 car garage as well as off-street parking. This 5-bedroom home has it all, new carpeting, new vinyl plank flooring, new heat pump, room for home occupation, multigenerational living, mini farm, or just large gatherings. Apple, cherry, and plum trees are the start of your orchard on the level sunny land. Possibilities are endless with this acreage (12 lots) more home sites? must check with the county.
